us<\/p> <a href=\"tel:9667684409\">9667684409<\/a>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"col col-md-6 animate-box\" data-animate-effect=\"fadeInUp\"> <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/garekarsmdskinclinic.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/Hair-mesotherapy.jpg\" alt=\"Mesotherapy hair treatment gurgaon\" class=\"mt-90 mb-30\"> <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/section>\r\n   <!-- Faqs -->\r\n   <section class=\"section-padding bg-cream\">\r\n    <div class=\"container\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">F.A.Qs<\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"section-title\"><h3>Mesotherapy Hair Treatment<\/h3><\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n                <ul class=\"accordion-box clearfix\">\r\n                    <li class=\"accordion block\">\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-btn\">     What is Mesotherapy?<\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"content\">\r\n                                <div class=\"text\">Mesotherapy is a non-invasive technique in which superficial injections are administered to inject the drug at the level of dermis.<\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/li>\r\n                    <li class=\"accordion block\">\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-btn\">  What is hair mesotherapy?   <\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"content\">\r\n                                <div class=\"text\">In case of hair injections of a solution containing a variety of minerals, vitamins, amino acids, and growth factors which are specific for hair growth are administered over the scalp.  <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/li>\r\n                    <li class=\"accordion block\">\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-btn\">  Are there any side effects?  <\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"content\">\r\n                                <div class=\"text\">Done under proper aseptic precautions, the procedure does not have any side effects. Pain during the procedure is also minimal.<\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/li>\r\n                    <li class=\"accordion block\">\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-btn\">    What are the main constituents of hair mesotherapy?  <\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"content\">\r\n                                <div class=\"text\">The main constituents are: Aminophylline, Glutathione, Chondroitin, Peptides, Growth factors, Adenosine, Zinc and Pyridoxine. <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/li>\r\n                    <li class=\"accordion block\">\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-btn\"> Who should undergo mesotherapy?<\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"content\">\r\n                                <div class=\"text\"><p>The procedure is suitable for hair loss in both males and females. You should consider mesotherapy if you suffer from any of the following:<\/p>\r\n                                    Progressive Balding<br>\r\n                                    Patchy Hair Loss<br>\r\n                                    Progressive Thinning of the Hair<\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/li>\r\n                    <li class=\"accordion block\">\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-btn\">    How much time does a session usually take?<\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"content\">\r\n                                <div class=\"text\">The procedure takes around 20-30 minutes. <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/li>\r\n                    <li class=\"accordion block\">\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-btn\"> What results can I expect from mesotherapy?<\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"acc-content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"content\">\r\n                                <div class=\"text\">Usually a minimum of 8-10 sessions are required to achieve hair growth. Initially the treatments are done every 2 weeks for the first 2 months. Thereafter the gaps are increased. You would notice a decrease in hair fall, increase in hair thickness and an increase in hair density as well.<\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                    <\/li>\r\n                   \r\n                <\/ul>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n<\/section>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Garekars MD Mesotherapy Hair Mesotherapy is here to stay, the procedure has a very high success rate and is virtually pain free and side effect free. The therapy is highly recommended, the procedure for the mesotherapy hair treatment involves injections of growth hormones into your scalp which will then boost hair growth in your follicles. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3210,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/garekarsmdskinclinic.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/55"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/garekarsmdskinclinic.com\/wp-json\